---

<BaseLayout title="Equipo — Loyal Bliss Productions">
  <Navigation />
  
  <main class="pt-20 min-h-screen">
    <section class="py-24 px-6">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        {/* Header */}
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
          <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">Nuestro Equipo</h1>
          <p class="text-lg text-bone/70 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
            Creativos apasionados dedicados a contar historias extraordinarias
          </p>
        </div>
        
        {/* Team Grid */}
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
          {team.map((member) => (
            <div class="group">
              <div class="relative aspect-[3/4] overflow-hidden rounded-xl mb-4">
                <img 
                  src={member.image} 
                  alt={member.name}
                  class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
                />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-coal/80 via-transparent to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity" />
                
                {/* Instagram link */}
                <a 
                  href={member.instagram}
                  target="_blank"
                  rel="noopener noreferrer"
                  class="absolute bottom-4 right-4 w-10 h-10 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full flex items-center justify-center opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-all hover:bg-white/20"
                >
                  <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M12 2.163c3.204 0 3.584.012 4.85.07 3.252.148 4.771 1.691 4.919 4.919.058 1.265.069 1.645.069 4.849 0 3.205-.012 3.584-.069 4.849-.149 3.225-1.664 4.771-4.919 4.919-1.266.058-1.644.07-4.85.07-3.204 0-3.584-.012-4.849-.07-3.26-.149-4.771-1.699-4.919-4.92-.058-1.265-.07-1.644-.07-4.849 0-3.204.013-3.583.07-4.849.149-3.227 1.664-4.771 4.919-4.919 1.266-.057 1.645-.069 4.849-.069zm0-2.163c-3.259 0-3.667.014-4.947.072-4.358.2-6.78 2.618-6.98 6.98-.059 1.281-.073 1.689-.073 4.948 0 3.259.014 3.668.072 4.948.2 4.358 2.618 6.78 6.98 6.98 1.281.058 1.689.072 4.948.072 3.259 0 3.668-.014 4.948-.072 4.354-.2 6.782-2.618 6.979-6.98.059-1.28.073-1.689.073-4.948 0-3.259-.014-3.667-.072-4.947-.196-4.354-2.617-6.78-6.979-6.98-1.281-.059-1.69-.073-4.949-.073zM5.838 12a6.162 6.162 0 1112.324 0 6.162 6.162 0 01-12.324 0zM12 16a4 4 0 110-8 4 4 0 010 8zm4.965-10.405a1.44 1.44 0 112.881.001 1.44 1.44 0 01-2.881-.001z"/>
                  </svg>
                </a>
              </div>
              
              <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-semibold mb-1">{member.name}</h3>
              <p class="text-gold text-sm mb-3">{member.role}</p>
              <p class="text-bone/60 text-sm leading-relaxed">{member.bio}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        
        {/* Culture Section */}
        <div class="mt-24 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
          <div>
            <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold mb-6">Nuestra Filosofía</h2>
            <p class="text-bone/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              En Loyal Bliss Productions, creemos que cada proyecto es una oportunidad 
              para crear algo único y memorable. Nos especializamos en narrativas visuales 
              que trascienden lo convencional.
            </p>
            <p class="text-bone/80 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
              Trabajamos con marcas y artistas que comparten nuestra visión de excelencia 
              y creatividad sin límites. Cada frame cuenta una historia, cada proyecto 
              deja una huella.
            </p>
            <p class="text-bone/80 leading-relaxed">
              Desde comerciales de alto impacto hasta fashion films vanguardistas, 
              nuestro compromiso es elevar cada producción al nivel de arte cinematográfico.
            </p>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative aspect-video rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
            <img 
              src="/media/images/cinema-1-cover.webp" 
              alt="Behind the scenes"
              class="w-full h-full object-cover"
            />
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-r from-coal/50 to-transparent" />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>